      • isSnapshot

        public static boolean isSnapshot()
        Indicates if this is a SNAPSHOT version. A SNAPSHOT version is a version under development that is not an official release.
        Returns:
        True if this is a snapshot version. False if it is a release version.

      • versionString

        public java.lang.String versionString()
        Prints the version string for this version of JavaGit.
        Returns:
        The version string in the format <MAJOR>.<MINOR>.<REVISION>-SNAPSHOT where <MAJOR> is the major version number, <MINOR> is the minor version number, <REVISION> is the revision number and -SNAPSHOT is the value inserted if this is a non-release version.
